{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-sistent-component-js-content-file-path-src-collections-sistent-components-divider-code-mdx","path":"/projects/sistent/components/divider/code","result":{"data":{"mdx":{"body":"\nimport { Divider, Box, List, ListItem, ListItemText, Chip, Stack } from \"@sistent/sistent\";\n\n\nThe Divider component is a thin, subtle line for separating content in your interface.\n\n<a id=\"Basic-Divider\">\n  <h2>Basic Divider</h2>\n</a>\n\nBy default, the Divider renders as a full-width horizontal line.\n\n<div className=\"showcase\">\n  <div className=\"items\">\n    <ThemeWrapper>\n      <Box sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n        <Divider />\n      </Box>\n    </ThemeWrapper>\n  </div>\n  <CodeBlock name=\"basic-divider\" collapsible code={`<Box sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n  <Divider />\n</Box>`} />\n</div>\n\n<a id=\"Variants\">\n  <h2>Variants</h2>\n</a>\n\nThe Divider supports three variants: `fullWidth` (default), `inset`, and `middle`.\n\n<div className=\"showcase\">\n  <div className=\"items\">\n    <ThemeWrapper>\n      <Box sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n        <Box sx={{ mb: 2 }}>Full Width:</Box>\n        <Divider variant=\"fullWidth\" />\n        <Box sx={{ my: 2 }}>Inset:</Box>\n        <Divider variant=\"inset\" />\n        <Box sx={{ my: 2 }}>Middle:</Box>\n        <Divider variant=\"middle\" />\n      </Box>\n    </ThemeWrapper>\n  </div>\n  <CodeBlock name=\"divider-variants\" collapsible code={`<Box sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n  <Divider variant=\"fullWidth\" />\n  <Divider variant=\"inset\" />\n  <Divider variant=\"middle\" />\n</Box>`} />\n</div>\n\n<a id=\"Vertical-Divider\">\n  <h2>Vertical Divider</h2>\n</a>\n\nUse `orientation=\"vertical\"` to render a vertical divider. The `flexItem` prop ensures proper height in flex containers.\n\n<div className=\"showcase\">\n  <div className=\"items\">\n    <ThemeWrapper>\n      <Box sx={{ display: \"flex\", alignItems: \"center\", gap: 2 }}>\n        <span>Left</span>\n        <Divider orientation=\"vertical\" flexItem />\n        <span>Center</span>\n        <Divider orientation=\"vertical\" flexItem />\n        <span>Right</span>\n      </Box>\n    </ThemeWrapper>\n  </div>\n  <CodeBlock name=\"vertical-divider\" collapsible code={`<Box sx={{ display: \"flex\", alignItems: \"center\", gap: 2 }}>\n  <span>Left</span>\n  <Divider orientation=\"vertical\" flexItem />\n  <span>Center</span>\n  <Divider orientation=\"vertical\" flexItem />\n  <span>Right</span>\n</Box>`} />\n</div>\n\n<a id=\"Divider-with-Text\">\n  <h2>Divider with Text</h2>\n</a>\n\nYou can render text or other elements within the divider using children. Use `textAlign` to control alignment.\n\n<div className=\"showcase\">\n  <div className=\"items\">\n    <ThemeWrapper>\n      <Box sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n        <Divider>CENTER</Divider>\n        <Box sx={{ my: 2 }} />\n        <Divider textAlign=\"left\">LEFT</Divider>\n        <Box sx={{ my: 2 }} />\n        <Divider textAlign=\"right\">RIGHT</Divider>\n        <Box sx={{ my: 2 }} />\n        <Divider>\n          <Chip label=\"Chip\" size=\"small\" />\n        </Divider>\n      </Box>\n    </ThemeWrapper>\n  </div>\n  <CodeBlock name=\"divider-with-text\" collapsible code={`<Box sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n  <Divider>CENTER</Divider>\n  <Divider textAlign=\"left\">LEFT</Divider>\n  <Divider textAlign=\"right\">RIGHT</Divider>\n  <Divider>\n    <Chip label=\"Chip\" size=\"small\" />\n  </Divider>\n</Box>`} />\n</div>\n\n<a id=\"List-Divider\">\n  <h2>List Divider</h2>\n</a>\n\nWhen using dividers in lists, set `component=\"li\"` to ensure valid HTML structure.\n\n<div className=\"showcase\">\n  <div className=\"items\">\n    <ThemeWrapper>\n      <List sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360, bgcolor: \"background.paper\" }}>\n        <ListItem>\n          <ListItemText primary=\"Inbox\" />\n        </ListItem>\n        <Divider component=\"li\" />\n        <ListItem>\n          <ListItemText primary=\"Drafts\" />\n        </ListItem>\n        <Divider component=\"li\" />\n        <ListItem>\n          <ListItemText primary=\"Trash\" />\n        </ListItem>\n      </List>\n    </ThemeWrapper>\n  </div>\n  <CodeBlock name=\"list-divider\" collapsible code={`<List sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n  <ListItem>\n    <ListItemText primary=\"Inbox\" />\n  </ListItem>\n  <Divider component=\"li\" />\n  <ListItem>\n    <ListItemText primary=\"Drafts\" />\n  </ListItem>\n  <Divider component=\"li\" />\n  <ListItem>\n    <ListItemText primary=\"Trash\" />\n  </ListItem>\n</List>`} />\n</div>\n\n<a id=\"Section-Separators\">\n  <h2>Section Separators</h2>\n</a>\n\nUse dividers to separate distinct sections in a layout, combined with proper spacing.\n\n<div className=\"showcase\">\n  <div className=\"items\">\n    <ThemeWrapper>\n      <Stack spacing={2} sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n        <Box sx={{ p: 2, bgcolor: \"background.paper\" }}>Section 1</Box>\n        <Divider />\n        <Box sx={{ p: 2, bgcolor: \"background.paper\" }}>Section 2</Box>\n        <Divider />\n        <Box sx={{ p: 2, bgcolor: \"background.paper\" }}>Section 3</Box>\n      </Stack>\n    </ThemeWrapper>\n  </div>\n  <CodeBlock name=\"section-dividers\" collapsible code={`<Stack spacing={2} sx={{ width: \"100%\", maxWidth: 360 }}>\n  <Box sx={{ p: 2 }}>Section 1</Box>\n  <Divider />\n  <Box sx={{ p: 2 }}>Section 2</Box>\n  <Divider />\n  <Box sx={{ p: 2 }}>Section 3</Box>\n</Stack>`} />\n</div>\n\n<a id=\"Icon-Grouping\">\n  <h2>Icon Grouping</h2>\n</a>\n\nUse vertical dividers with the `middle` variant to group related actions in toolbars.\n\n<div className=\"showcase\">\n  <div className=\"items\">\n    <ThemeWrapper>\n      <Box sx={{ display: \"flex\", alignItems: \"center\", gap: 1 }}>\n        <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Bold</Box>\n        <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Italic</Box>\n        <Divider orientation=\"vertical\" variant=\"middle\" flexItem />\n        <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Left</Box>\n        <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Center</Box>\n        <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Right</Box>\n      </Box>\n    </ThemeWrapper>\n  </div>\n  <CodeBlock name=\"icon-grouping\" collapsible code={`<Box sx={{ display: \"flex\", alignItems: \"center\", gap: 1 }}>\n  <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Bold</Box>\n  <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Italic</Box>\n  <Divider orientation=\"vertical\" variant=\"middle\" flexItem />\n  <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Left</Box>\n  <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Center</Box>\n  <Box sx={{ p: 1 }}>Right</Box>\n</Box>`} />\n</div>\n","frontmatter":{"title":"Divider Code","description":"The `Divider` component renders a thin line that separates content within lists, layouts, and sections, providing a subtle way to reinforce visual hierarchy."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/sistent/components/divider/code","componentName":"divider","availablePages":["code","guidance","overview"],"frontmatter":{"title":"Divider Code","component":"divider","description":"The `Divider` component renders a thin line that separates content within lists, layouts, and sections, providing a subtle way to reinforce visual hierarchy."}}},"staticQueryHashes":["4152005505","934084603"],"slicesMap":{}}